<headline>Winter Weather Advisory issued January 06 at 12:02PM EST until January 06 at 10:00PM EST by NWS Albany</headline>
<description>...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 PM EST THIS
EVENING...
* WHAT...Snow. Additional snow accumulations of up to 3 inches.
* WHERE...Northern Herkimer County.
* WHEN...Until 10 PM EST this evening.
* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions and low visibility. A
lake effect snow band will fluctuate from Old Forge northward.</description>
<instruction>Slow down and use caution while traveling.</instruction>
